  <p>The University of Michigan Library is dedicated to creating inclusive services and products for all users. See more about our approach to <a href="https://www.lib.umich.edu/about-us/about-library/accessibility/digital-product-accessibility">digital product accessibility</a>, as well as our overall <a href="https://lib.umich.edu/about-us/about-library/accessibility">accessibility services</a> and practices at the U-M Library.</p>
