  <p>The next scheduled accessibility evaluation for this product is in January 2027.</p>
  <h2>Feedback and support</h2>
  <p>We welcome your feedback and will do our best to resolve any issues promptly.</p>
  <p>If you encounter any accessibility issues while using this product or have questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:design-discovery@umich.edu">design-discovery@umich.edu</a>.</p>
